hifi.changeCellularSettings: Usethe Amasethingi akho ukuthi adlale umculo Phezulu kakhulu noma phansi lapho usakaza. Ukuze ushintshe lokhu, iya kokuthi Amasethingi bese ukhetha i-HiFi ukuze uthole Ikhwalithi yokusakaza.
hifi.optOutOfDowngrade: Usukhubazé isici sekhwalithi esizilungisa sona Kumasethingi. Lokhu kusho ukuthi ungase uphazamiseke ekulaleleni kwakho uma une-bandwidth ebuthaka ye-inthanethi.
hifi.poorBandwidthInterferes: Kubonakala sengathi i-bandwidth yakho ye-inthanethi inenkinga yokusekela i-HiFi njangamanje. Zama ukuhlola ukuxhuma kwakho noma ushintshele kunethiwekhi ehlukile.
hifi.defaultToVeryHigh: Ayikho into embi njengalapho ingoma yeqa lapho usuyijabulela khona. Yingakho sikwehlisa ngokuzenzakalelayo kusuka ku-HiFi uye kukhwalithi yomsindo ephansi uma une-bandwidth ebuthaka.
hifi.needToReDownload: Izingoma osuzidawunilodile azikho okwamanje ku-HiFi. Uma ufuna ukuzilalela ku-HiFi, uzodinga ukuzidawuniloda kabusha. Ungakhohlwa phela ukuthi amafayela ezingoma ze-HiFi makhulu futhi angasebenzisa isitoreji esikhulu.
hifi.bluetoothDegradesHifi: Ukulalela i-HiFi usebenzisa i-Bluetooth kukuvumela ukuthi ujabulele ikhwalithi ephezulu yomsindo kunaleyo etholakala ku-Spotify Ekhokhelwayo kuphela. I-HiFi ijatshulelwa kangcono ngezipikha zokuXhuma ku-Spotify ze-{0} kanye/noma amadivayisi anezintambo.
hifi.songNotAvailable: The song you're trying to listen to is not available in HiFi at this time.
